# 🎓 Student Management System (Java + MySQL + JDBC)

A simple console-based Java application to manage student records using a MySQL database and JDBC. It supports CRUD operations such as Add, View, Find, Update, and Delete students.

---

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- Java 8
- MySQL
- JDBC
- MySQL Connector/J
- Console I/O

---

## 📁 Project Structure
project/
├── src/
│ ├── config/ # DB configuration
│ ├── dao/ # DAO interfaces and implementations
│ ├── entity/ # Student model
│ ├── service/ # Business logic
│ └── ui/ # Console UI
├── lib/ # MySQL JDBC jar (e.g., mysql-connector-j-9.3.0.jar)
├── resources/ # DB properties
└── out/ # Compiled .class files

📋 Features
- Add a new student
- View all students
- Search student by ID
- Update student details
- Delete student
- MySQL-backed persistence

Developed as part of Week 4 of Jeev Internship Program
